Error.Message:
Chineseletter:1~2
產生物件後需要正確使用物件資料
public ChineseLetter(String title,String receiver,String content,String sender,String date)
{
this.title = title;
this.receiver = receiver;
this.content = content;
this.sender = sender;
this.date = date;
}
public String getReceiver()
{
return receiver;
}
public String getSender()
{
return sender;
}
public String getDate()
{
return date;
}
以及物件動作
public void display()
{
System.out.printIn(receiver + " "  + title + ",您好");
System.out.printIn(content);
System.out.printIn(sender + " 敬上");
System.out.printIn(date);
}
